<noinclude>
One row of `ChapterTable`. Receives projected subobject values via
SMW's `format=template | named args=yes`. The leading newline inside
`<includeonly>` is load-bearing: SMW concatenates row-template
invocations with no separator, so without it the `|-` row separator
would land on the same line as the previous row's last cell and
MediaWiki's wikitable parser would collapse everything into a single
row.
